      <p>
        Nouns express the names of people or objects. Proper nouns include place names and the names of people.  
        Some monosyllabic nouns can be repeated to indicate every individual in a group, such
        as <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5912'>人人</a> (everyone), 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=434'>天</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=434'>天</a> (every day), and so on.
      </p>
