      <p>
        The nouns of location <a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐ', 'inside')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a> and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=585' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'the position on or above something')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>上</a>
        are often used after other nouns. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9371' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '腦袋 nǎodài', 'head / skull / brains')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">脑袋</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=584' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shàng', 'above / previous')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">上</a> (on your head), <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9372' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lùshang', 'on the road / on a journey / road surface')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">路上</a> (on the road),
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=922' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shǒu', 'hand')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">手</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐ', 'inside')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a> (in hand), <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9373' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'pocket')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">兜</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐ', 'inside')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a> (in my pocket), and so on.
        However, you cannot use the word <a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐ', 'inside')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a> after a geographic place names.
        When a noun of location is acting as the predicate or adverbial adjection <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a> 
        is not needed.  For example, in the sentence <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1258' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fángzi', 'house')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">房子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐ', 'inside')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5979' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jià', 'frame / rack / framework')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">架</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4190' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '鋼琴 gāngqín', 'piano')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">钢琴</a>  (There is a piano in the house), there is no <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a> before <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1258' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fángzi', 'house')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">房子</a>.
      </p>
