        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>。 
      </p>
      <p>
        Some adjectives can be repeated to intensify their degree. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=519' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'she her')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">她</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4167' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '頭髮 tóufa', 'hair on the head')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">头发</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1322' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '長 zhǎng', 'director / chief / head / elder')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">长</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1322' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '長 zhǎng', 'director / chief / head / elder')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">长</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a>。(Her hair is very long.) Adjectives can be used in front 
        of verbs to act as abverbial adjuncts. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2888' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '熱情 rèqíng', 'cordial / enthusiastic')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">热情</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dì', 'earth / ground / place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">地</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9482' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiēdài', 'to receive a visitor / to admit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">接待</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=366' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '我們 wǒmen', 'we')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我们</a>。
        (He cordially received us.) The adverbial adjunct is <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2888' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '熱情 rèqíng', 'cordial / enthusiastic')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">热情</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=803' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dì', 'earth / ground / place')" 
