      <p>
        Auxiliary verbs can modify verbs or adjectives. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=567' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '會 huì', 'can / be possible / be able to / to assemble / to meet')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">会</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5243' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '講 jiǎng', 'to speak / to explain')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讲</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9418' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '國語 Guóyǔ', 'Mandarin')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">国语</a> (I can speak Mandarin). In this sentence the auxiliary verb 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=606' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huì會 huì', 'able to')" 
        onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>会</a> (can) modifies the verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5243' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '講 jiǎng', 'to speak / to explain')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">讲</a> (speak).
        For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9444' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '圖書館 túshūguǎn', 'library')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">图书馆</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=407' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '裡 lǐ', 'inside')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">里</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5660' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '應該 yīnggāi', 'ought to / should / must')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">应该</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9443' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '安靜 ānjìng', 'quiet / peaceful / calm')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">安静</a>  (The library should be quiet).
        In this sentence the auxiliary verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=5660' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '應該 yīnggāi', 'ought to / should / must')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">应该</a> (should) modifies the adjective
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9443' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '安靜 ānjìng', 'quiet / peaceful / calm')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">安静</a> (quiet).
      </p>
