      <p>
        Measure words are used after numbers and demonstrative pronouns. For example,<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=825' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '買 mǎi', 'to buy')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">买</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9533' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '輛 liàng', 'measure word for vehicles')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">辆</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2987' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '自行車 zìxíngchē', 'bicycle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">自行车</a> 
        (I bought a bicycle). The measure word is <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9533' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '輛 liàng', 'measure word for vehicles')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">辆</a> and 
        the number is <a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a>. Another example is, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'měi', 'each / every')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">每</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=667' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cì', 'time')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">次</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8875' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '看見 kànjiàn', 'to see')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">看见</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" 
