        demonstrative pronoun is <a href='/word_detail.php?id=963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'měi', 'each / every')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">每</a> (every).
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9333' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '重疊 chóngdié', 'to duplicate / to repeat')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">重叠</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9278' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '量詞 liàngcí', 'measure word')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">量词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'měi', 'each / every')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">每</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5246' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yìsi', 'idea / opinion / meaning')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">意思</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9478' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '聰明 cōngming', 'clever / intelligent / bright / smart / acute')" 
