      <p>
        Repeating measure words indicates “every.” For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9478' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '聰明 cōngming', 'clever / intelligent / bright / smart / acute')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">聪明</a> 
        (every one of them is clever).
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9299' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngliàngcí', 'nominal measure word')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名量词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9288' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'míngcí', 'noun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">名词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiánbian', 'front')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">前边</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=857' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shùliàng', 'quantity')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数量</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shìwù', 'thing / object')" 
