        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">看</a><a href='ref_measure_words.htm'>常见名量词表</a>。
      </p>
      <p>
        Nominal measure words are used in front of nouns to describe quantities of objects.
        See <a href='ref_measure_words.htm'>List of Common Nominal Measure Words</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9300' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動量詞 dòngliàngcí', 'verbal measure word')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动量词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=509' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '與 yǔ', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">与</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=857' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '數量 shùliàng', 'quantity')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数量</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動作 dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" 
