        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">回</a>”。“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=667' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cì', 'time')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">次</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9313' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tàng', 'a time / a trip')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">趟</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=3548' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huí', 'to go back / to turn around / to answer / to return / to revolve')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">回</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=757' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dōu', 'all')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">都</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9300' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動量詞 dòngliàngcí', 'verbal measure word')" 
