        For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=714' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīntiān', 'today')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">今天</a><span class='hl'>又</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9313' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tàng', 'a time / a trip')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">趟</a>。(We have already left.) <a href='/word_detail.php?id=368' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'again / once more / re- / second / another')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">再</a> is used for future actions. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=366' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒmen', 'we')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我们</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=502' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bù', 'not / no')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=567' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huì', 'can / be possible / be able to / to assemble / to meet')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">会</a><span class='hl'>再</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8875' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kànjiàn', 'to see')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">看见</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=518' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tā', 'he him')" 
