      <p>
        Prepositions are placed in front of nouns or pronouns to form prepositional phrases expressing
        the exclusion, comparison, being acted on, mode, cause, object, direction, place, or time
        of an action. Expressing time, place, and direction include 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1383' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cóng', 'from')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">从</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=526' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàng', 'towards / to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">向</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=733' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǎng', 'to go (in a direction)')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">往</a>. Prepositions indicating an object are 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2021' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēn', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">跟</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=723' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duì', 'to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">对</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=775' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gěi', 'to / for / for the benefit of / to give')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">给</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1744' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duìyú', 'regarding / with regards to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">对于</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guānyú', 'pertaining to / concerning / regarding')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">关于</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1530' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǎ', 'marker for direct-object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">把</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1069' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lián', 'even')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">连</a>. Prepositions expressing a cause include
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=372' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'for / to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">为</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=8866' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèile', 'in order to / for the purpose of / so as to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">为了</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2192' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóuyú', 'due to / as a result of / because of / owing to')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由于</a>.
        Prepositions expressing mode are
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2750' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ànzhào', 'according to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">按照</a> and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2562' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gēnjù', 'basis / foundation')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">根据</a>.
        Prepositions expressing the passive are 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=426' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bèi', 'by')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">被</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=5688' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiào', 'to call / to yell / to be called / to order')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">叫</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=770' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ràng', 'to allow')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">让</a>.
        Prepositions expressing comparison include <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1303' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bì', 'to associate with / be near')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比</a>.
        Prepositions expressing exclusion include 
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=622' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chú', 'except')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">除</a> and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16950' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chúle', 'except')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">除了</a>.
      </p>
