        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">书</a>”。
      </p>
      <p>
        When the particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'aspectual particle')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a> follow a verb it indicates that an action has been completed.
        For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=825' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mǎi', 'to buy')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">买</a><span class='hl'>了</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=923' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'běn', 'measure word for books')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">本</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2543' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shū', 'book')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">书</a>。 (I bought a book.)
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngtài zhùcí', 'aspectual particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动态助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=829' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guò', 'to cross / to go over / to pass')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1943' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fù', 'to add / to attach / to be close to / to be attached')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">附</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1860' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dòngzuò', 'movement / motion / action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动作</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=820' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǐjīng', 'already')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">已经</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1068' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guòqu', '(in the) past / former')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过去</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><span class='hl'>过</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=117' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Měiguó', 'United States')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">美国</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=751' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'méiyǒu', 'to not have / there is not')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">没有</a>？”
      </p>
      <p>
        The aspectual particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=829' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'guò', 'to cross / to go over / to pass')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">过</a> is placed after a verb to indicate that the action happened in 
        the past. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><span class='hl'>过</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=117' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Měiguó', 'United States')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">美国</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=751' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'méiyǒu', 'to not have / there is not')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">没有</a>？ (Have you ever been to the United States?)
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1943' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fù', 'to add / to attach / to be close to / to be attached')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">附</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16958' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mòwěi', 'tip / extremity')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末尾</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1316' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gèzhǒng', 'every kind of / all kinds / various kinds')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">各种</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9308' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔqì', 'tone / manner of speaking / mood')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ma', 'indicates question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>”（ma）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a>”（ne）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4980' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ba', '...right? / ...OK?')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吧</a>”（ba）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>”（le）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>”（a）。
      </p>
      <p>
        Modal particles are placed at the end of a sentence to express a mood.
        The modal particles are <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ma', 'indicates question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>（ma），<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a>（ne），<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4980' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ba', '...right? / ...OK?')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吧</a>（ba），<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>（le），<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>（a）.
