      <p>
        The modal particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a> has the following uses
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a> can be placed at the end of an affirmative / negative
          question to indicate uncertainty.
          For example,  <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=825' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mǎi', 'to buy')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">买</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=502' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bù', 'not / no')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=825' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mǎi', 'to buy')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">买</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2543' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shū', 'book')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">书</a><span 
          class='hl'>呢</span>？
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a> can be placed at the tail of a sentence with an 
          interrogative pronoun to indicate conjecture.
          For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3794' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shéi', 'who')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谁</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2087' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cuòwù', 'error / mistake')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">错误</a><span 
          class='hl'>呢</span>？
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a> can be used in a question with an alternative to indicate a 
          tone of interrogation.  For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=13542' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xuékē', 'discipline')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">学科</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xué', 'to study / to learn')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">学</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1141' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'háishì', 'still / nevertheless')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">还是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3924' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xué', 'to study / to learn')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">学</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6280' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wénxué', 'literature')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">文学</a><span class='hl'>呢</span>？
          (Are you studying science or are you studying arts?)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a> can be appended to a noun or pronoun to ask a one-member
          question. For example,
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=264' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiànzài', 'at present / in the process of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">现在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=366' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒmen', 'we')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我们</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3548' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huí', 'to go back / to turn around / to answer / to return / to revolve')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">回</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=745' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiā', 'family / home')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">家</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><span class='hl'>呢</span>？
          (We are going home.  And you?)
