          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a> can be used at the end of an alternative style question, a affirmative-negative question,  or
          a question with an interrogative pronoun to indicate an interrogative tone.
          For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3368' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zuò', 'to sit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">坐</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3966' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chē', 'vehicle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">车</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1141' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'háishì', 'still / nevertheless')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">还是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4954' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dǎ', 'to beat / to strike / to hit / to type / to mix up / to fetch / to shoot / to calculate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">打</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3966' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chē', 'vehicle')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">车</a><span class='hl'>啊</span>？ (Are you going to catch a bus or [wave down] a taxi?)
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9224' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiàmian', 'lower side / below / next / the following')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下面</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8533' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòngtú', 'use / application')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用途</a>：
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16958' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mòwěi', 'tip / extremity / end')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末尾</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1178' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chūxiàn', 'to appear / to arise / to emerge')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">出现</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=798' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xīn', 'new')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">新</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=499' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qíngkuàng', 'circumstances / state of affairs / situation')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">情况</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9347' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wàibian', 'outside')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">外边</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3200' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔ', 'rain')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">雨</a><span class='hl'>了</span>”。
        </li>
        <li>
          “<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16958' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mòwěi', 'tip / extremity / end')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末尾</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3088' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tíxǐng', 'to remind / to call attention to / to warn of')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">提醒</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=13096' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'quàngào', 'to advise')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">劝告</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16964' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cuīcù', 'to urge')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">催促</a>。
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        The structural particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a> has the following uses. 
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a> can be used at the end of a sentence to indicate a newly
          emerged condition. For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9347' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wàibian', 'outside')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">外边</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=580' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xià', 'next')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">下</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3200' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔ', 'rain')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">雨</a><span class='hl'>了</span>。 (It has started to rain outside.)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a> may be used at the end of a sentence to indicate a reminder,
          advice, or urging.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ma', 'indicates a question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=16775' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǐnéng', 'can only / obliged to do something')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">只能</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16958' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mòwěi', 'tip / extremity / end')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末尾</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1993' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gòuchéng', 'to constitute / to form / to compose')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">构成</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6445' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yíwèn', 'to question / to query')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10224' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fānyì', 'to translate / to interpret')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">翻译</a><span class='hl'>吗</span>？”
      </p>
      <p>
        The modal particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ma', 'indicates a question')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a> can only be used at the end of a declarative sentence to
        form a question. <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10224' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fānyì', 'to translate / to interpret')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">翻译</a><span class='hl'>吗</span>？ (Are you a translator?)
      </p>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='interjections'></a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9293' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tàncí', 'interjection / exclamation')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">叹词</a>
        Interjections
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9293' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tàncí', 'interjection / exclamation')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">叹词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16941' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gǎntàn', 'to sigh')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huòzhě', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或者</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=7922' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hūhuàn', 'to call out / to shout')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呼唤</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16965' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yìngdá', 'to reply')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">应答</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6552' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to feed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">喂</a>” （wèi）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9318' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'en', 'expresses approval, appreciation or agreement')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">嗯</a>”（èn）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>”（à）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9317' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'āiyā', 'expresses wonder, shock or admiration')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哎呀</a>”（āiyā）、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=12973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ō', 'Oh!')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">噢</a>”（ō）、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=7397' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ó', 'oh is that so')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哦</a>（ó）。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9293' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tàncí', 'interjection / exclamation')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">叹词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1783' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yībān', 'same / ordinary / common / general')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一般</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=613' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiánmiàn', 'in front of / facing')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">前面</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=697' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dànshì', 'but')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">但是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=502' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bù', 'not / no')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1263' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'néng', 'can / able')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">能</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2769' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jùzi', 'sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9259' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéngfèn', 'ingredient / element')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">成分</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6052' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lìrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">例如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        Interjections express an exclamation, a call, or a response.
        For example, <a href='/word_detail.php?id=6552' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèi', 'to feed')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">喂</a>（wèi）、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9318' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'en', 'expresses approval, appreciation or agreement')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">嗯</a>（èn）、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>（à）、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9317' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'āiyā', 'expresses wonder, shock or admiration')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哎呀</a>（āiyā）、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=12973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ō', 'Oh!')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">噢</a>”（ō）、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=7397' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ó', 'oh is that so')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哦</a>（ó）. Interjections are most often used at the start of 
        a sentence but do not act as an element of the sentence. For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>喂</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=762' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎo', 'small / young')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3235' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Wáng', 'Wang')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">王</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ma', 'indicates a question')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>？ [Hello.  Are you Xiao Wang?] （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4954' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dǎ', 'to beat / to strike / to hit / to type / to mix up / to fetch / to shoot / to calculate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">打</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '電話 diànhuà', 'telephone / phone call')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">电话</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=7922' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '呼喚 hūhuàn', 'to call out / to shout')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呼唤</a>）(Making a telephone, expressing a greeting.)
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>嗯</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=762' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'xiǎo', 'small / young')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">小</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3235' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Wáng', 'Wang')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">王</a>。 [Yes.  I am Xiao Wang.] （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10560' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '答應 dāying', 'to promise / to reply / to respond / to agree')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">答应</a>）[Expressing a response]
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>哎呀</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9489' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yīfu', 'clothes')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">衣服</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6696' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shī', 'moist / wet')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">湿</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>。 [Oh my! My clothes are wet.] （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=12663' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīngyà', 'amazed / astonished / surprised / amazing')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">惊讶</a>）(Expressing surprise)
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>啊</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=5024' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'měilì', 'beautiful')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">美丽</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=7716' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fēngjǐng', 'scenery / landscape')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">风景</a>。[Ah! What a beautiful scene.] (<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16665' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zàntàn', 'to sigh or gasp in admiration / to praise highly')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">赞叹</a>) (Expressing admiration)
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>唉</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6289' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mǎshàng', 'immediately')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">马上</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=902' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiù', 'right away / only')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">就</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǒu', 'to walk / to go / to move / to leave')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">走</a>。 [OK! I will go right away.] 
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10560' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dāying', 'to promise / to reply / to respond / to agree')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">答应</a>）
          (Indicating a response)
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>哦</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=321' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wǒ', 'I / me')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">我</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2678' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cuò', 'mistake / error / blunder / fault')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">错</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>。 [Oh! My mistake.]
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=12846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lǐnghuì', 'to understand / to comprehend / to grasp')" 
