        </li>
        <li>
          <span class='hl'>噢</span>！<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1254' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yuánlái', 'originally / formerly')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">原来</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a>。 [Oh! It was you all along.]
          （<a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1437' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'liǎojiě', 'to understand / to realize')" 
